{
  "stem": "14251.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, some of them had difficulties with their parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was becoming apparent this was not a way for me to stay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The other thing that happened is things were becoming very difficult for my parents, because they insisted on staying together, but on their own, not through places provided by these rescuers.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They helped with food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they helped with some money and ration stamps and things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they could not provide places.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They insisted to them that they should separate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would not do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father hit on the idea to go as soldier on furlough and rent a room and be alone with his 'girlfriend.' And that seemed to work, except after two or three days you had that form to fill out.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, they remembered Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], the lawyer of the Levents, who could make all things happen in this universe and would take the forms to him and have him fill them out and get them back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that worked for a little while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But if you can imagine, you have to be concerned about your haircut, not looking like a vagrant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Your shoes mustn't be walked down, because in that country you keep your shoes orderly, clean, the heels healed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You don't look like a schlumper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The look that you now pay a lot of money for to look like was not in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was terribly important, because there were also people like Stela Goldschlog, who was a Berlin, German Jew, 21 years old, who had become one of the main informers in that city for the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't judge it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Yes, no, good, bad, I'm not here for that part.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She had a knack for recognizing people living underground.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
